message.content:
Here is a sample healthy meal plan for the week that meets your dietary restrictions:
Monday - Chicken Salad with mixed greens, grilled chicken breast, apple slices, walnuts and a balsamic vinaigrette.
Tuesday - Grilled Tofu with brown rice, steamed broccoli, carrots and teriyaki sauce.
Wednesday - Black Bean Burritos with black beans, corn, red peppers, avocado and salsa.
Thursday - Baked Salmon with wild rice, asparagus, cherry tomatoes and lemon butter sauce.
Friday - Vegetable Stir Fry with broccoli florets, carrots, mushrooms, green beans and a light soy sauce.
